歌曲由阿黛尔和制作者{{le|格鲁·克鲁斯汀|Greg Kurstin}}共同谱写，格鲁负责演奏贝斯、吉他、钢琴和键盘，阿黛尔打鼓<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6738449/radio-on-adele-hello-she-can-make-you-feel-what-she-feels|title=Radio on Adele's 'Hello': 'She Can Make You Feel What She Feels'|work=Billboard|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2015-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025123813/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6738449/radio-on-adele-hello-she-can-make-you-feel-what-she-feels|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿黛尔曾表示她喜欢在家创作她的音乐，但这次有点非比寻常，歌曲是在[[伦敦|伦敦]][[奇斯威克|奇斯威克]]完成的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p035zwgc|title=Adele: "My son doesn't like my music, I just sing Twinkle Twinkle"|publisher=BBC Radio 2|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2015-10-24|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124122112/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p035zwgc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲的创作过程很慢，花了六个月才完成。起初阿黛尔和克鲁斯汀着手谱写第一段；歌曲完成一半，六个月后阿黛尔拜訪克鲁斯汀，要他跟她一起完成歌曲，库鲁斯特表示他不确定“阿黛尔是否曾打算回过头来完成它”<ref name="RTm">{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-inside-her-private-life-and-triumphant-return-20151103?page=2|title=Adele: Inside Her Private Life and Triumphant Return|author=Brian Hiatt|work=Rolling Stone|date=2015-11-03|accessdate=2015-11-04|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117065140/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-inside-her-private-life-and-triumphant-return-20151103?page=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

歌曲是一首[[灵魂乐|灵魂乐]]钢琴謠曲，以[[F小调|F小调]]演奏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stereogum.com/1839280/adele-hello-video/mp3s/|title=Adele – "Hello" Video|work=Stereogum|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-date=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211091516/http://www.stereogum.com/1839280/adele-hello-video/mp3s/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vulture.com/2015/10/adele-hello-single-cant-be-bothered-with-modern-technology.html|title=Adele's 'Hello' Rebuffs Modern Technology|work=Vulture|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117022400/http://www.vulture.com/2015/10/adele-hello-single-cant-be-bothered-with-modern-technology.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，速度为每分钟79拍<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.audiokeychain.com/track/vqs/adele-hello|title = Key and BPM of Adele – Hello|website = AudioKeychain|accessdate = 2015-11-21|archive-date = 2015-11-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151122134323/https://www.audiokeychain.com/track/vqs/adele-hello|dead-url = no}}</ref>。主歌段可听到重复的钢琴和弦，紧接着Fm–A{{音符|flat}}–E{{音符|flat}}–D{{音符|flat}}和弦進程<ref name="sheet music">{{cite web|title=Adele "Hello" official sheet music|url=http://www.sheetmusicdirect.com/se/ID_No/122316/Product.aspx|website=Sheet Music Direct|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611194341/https://www.sheetmusicdirect.com/se/ID_No/122316/Product.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Adele "Hello" official sheet music Musicnotes|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0156888|website=Musicnotes|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722022746/https://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0156888|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據歌曲在Musicnotes.com上的樂譜，阿黛尔的音域从F<sub>3</sub>跨越到A♭<sub>5</sub><ref name=Vocalrange>{{cite web|title=Hello By Adele – Digital Sheet Music|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0156888|website=musicnotes.com|publisher=Musicnotes, Inc|accessdate=2015-10-26|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722022746/https://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0156888|dead-url=no}}</ref>。副歌部分可以听到阿黛尔演唱句子时的声音盖过和音、钢琴和鼓声层面，后三者被《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》形容为“朝着非常甜美的声墙”倾斜<ref name="telegraph"/>。歌曲还包含被认为是阿黛尔提供的鼓声<ref name="Billboard - Lars">{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6738252/adele-comeback-song-hello-25|title=Adele's Comeback Song 'Hello' Has Arrived|last=Brandle|first=Lars|work=Billboard|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2015-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108145432/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6738252/adele-comeback-song-hello-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

歌词方面，歌曲聚-{}-焦于怀旧和遗憾的主题，以谈话方式展现出。这被看作是延续了她的单曲《[[Someone_like_You_(阿黛尔歌曲)|Someone like You]]》所反映的失败戀情的主题。歌词可以看成是对话性质的，围绕着“她过去所有的人际关系，从朋友、家人到前合作伙伴”兜转<Ref>
{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/music/feature/a675199/adeles-new-single-first-listen-review-hello-is-a-mighty-comeback/#|title=Adele's new single first listen review: 'Hello' is a mighty comeback|author=Lewis Corner|work=Digital Spy|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2015-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151214011935/http://www.digitalspy.com/music/feature/a675199/adeles-new-single-first-listen-review-hello-is-a-mighty-comeback/|dead-url=no}}
</ref>。在谈到歌词内容时，阿黛尔告诉BBC广播一台《早餐秀》（{{lang|en|Breakfast Show}}）主持人尼克·格里姆肖（{{lang|en|Nick Grimshaw}}）：“我觉得我们所有人都在不断往前发展，歌曲并不是关于过去的关系、感情关系的，它关于我与我所爱每一个人的关系。这并不是说我们已经破裂了，我们都得到了我们正在过的生活，我需要写这首歌好让他们都听听，因为我跟他们已经断交了<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/adele-fame-toxic-touring-lonelypeople-6693239|title=Adele: Fame is toxic and touring is lonely...people have paid to see me but what if they don't like me|author=Rachael Bletchly|date=2015-10-23|work=mirror|accessdate=2015-10-25|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722022804/https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/adele-fame-toxic-touring-lonelypeople-6693239|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”阿黛尔表示，歌词“宛如天外的问候”（{{lang|en|Hello from the other side}}）意味着“长大成人的另一个侧面，它使得你从青少年时代末期走向二十出头<ref name="RTm"/>”。

== 发行与评价 ==
10月18日，歌曲的30秒片段在《[[英国版X音素|英国版X音素]]》的一段广告中表演。这段广告预告片是当时的新素材，歌词在黑屏上跟她的声音一同出现<ref>{{Cite web|title = Adele 'teases new material in TV advert'|url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-34567653|publisher = BBC News|accessdate = 2015-10-26|archive-date = 2020-11-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201129094528/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-34567653|dead-url = no}}</ref>。主打单曲的30秒首播过后，网民和阿黛尔的歌迷们表示十分激動，就连《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》的杰森·梅里特（{{lang|en|Jason Merritt}}）也认为阿黛尔“困扰住这个星球”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/10/adele-teaser-x-factor-commerical|title=Adele's Mysterious New Teaser Has Stymied a Planet|author=Josh Duboff|work=Vanity Fair|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722022810/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/10/adele-teaser-x-factor-commerical|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月22日，阿黛尔透过[[Twitter|Twitter]]上的一封献给歌迷的亲笔信中宣布《[[25_(愛黛兒專輯)|25]]》即将发布<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/34606780/adele-reveals-the-release-date-for-her-third-studio-album-25-and-new-single |title=Adele reveals the release date for her third studio album, 25, and new single |publisher=BBC |date=2015-10-22 |accessdate=2015-10-22 |archive-date=2015-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151023054940/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/34606780/adele-reveals-the-release-date-for-her-third-studio-album-25-and-new-single |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=CoS>{{cite web|last1=Geslani|first1=Michelle|title=Adele confirms new album is titled 25, first single coming next week|url=http://consequenceofsound.net/2015/10/adele-confirms-november-20th-release-for-new-album-25/|website=Consequence of Sound|accessdate=2015-10-25|archive-date=2015-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024220300/http://consequenceofsound.net/2015/10/adele-confirms-november-20th-release-for-new-album-25/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=AXS>{{cite web|last1=Hunt|first1=Chase|title=Adele announces new album '25'; new single 'Hello' out Oct. 23|url=http://www.axs.com/adele-announces-new-album-25-new-single-hello-out-oct-23-68588|website=AXS|accessdate=2015-10-25|archive-date=2019-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621220000/https://www.axs.com/adele-announces-new-album-25-new-single-hello-out-oct-23-68588|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她还表示歌曲将于10月23日作为专辑的主打单曲发行。发行当日，阿黛尔参加BBC广播一台的尼克·格里姆肖为歌曲首演准备的节目<ref>{{Cite web|title = Adele premieres 'intimate' new song|url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-34613748|publisher = BBC News|accessdate = 2015-10-26|archive-date = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131408/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-34613748|dead-url = no}}</ref><nowiki/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p035ztl5|title=BBC Radio 1 – The Radio 1 Breakfast Show with Nick Grimshaw, Adele Is in the Building With Her New Song, Adele tears up introducing her new song 'Hello' on BBC Radio 1|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007035818/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p035ztl5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

歌曲一经发行，就获得音评人好评。《[[卫报|卫报]]》的{{le|亚历克西斯·彼得里迪斯|Alexis Petridis}}称歌曲是“一首很不错的民谣，但是流派中的典范”，并认为“准确来讲，这种史诗级失恋民谣使得阿黛尔成为世界上最伟大的明星之一<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2015/oct/23/adele-new-single-hello-review|title=Striking, witty and lovelorn – Adele's new single Hello reviewed (and hear it here, too)|last=Petridis|first=Alexis|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108155329/http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2015/oct/23/adele-new-single-hello-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[独立报|独立报]]》的艾蜜丽·捷普（{{lang|en|Emily Jupp}}）在她的评论中表示歌曲“可能不是开创性的，但阿黛尔带着她的密友回归，萦绕耳畔的声音非常的受欢迎。”她假设“如果这不是一首糟糕的民谣”，“阿黛尔就发挥了她的最高水准，带出感情上的爱情传奇，但跟她的上一张专辑《[[二十一歲|21]]》遗失的同样多，但是这一次，自我宽恕有点多<ref>{{cite news|last1=Jupp|first1=Emily|title=Adele 'Hello', first review: This is an 'if it ain't broke' ballad showing what Adele does best|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/adele-hello-first-listen-review-this-is-an-if-it-aint-broke-ballad-showing-what-adele-does-best-a6705686.html|accessdate=2015-10-23|newspaper=The Independent|date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722024510/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/adele-hello-first-listen-review-this-is-an-if-it-aint-broke-ballad-showing-what-adele-does-best-a6705686.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。”

《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》的{{le|格雷格·科特|Greg Kot}}写道：“歌词在放大个人细节以配合她的声音力量和克制力的结合体时发挥了最大的作用<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kot|first1=Greg|title=Adele's new song 'Hello' a safe balancing act|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/music/kot/ct-adele-new-song-hello-20151022-column.html|accessdate=2015-10-23|newspaper=Chicago Tribune|date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116131901/https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/music/kot/ct-adele-new-song-hello-20151022-column.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的尼尔·麦考密克（{{lang|en|Neil McCormick}}）称歌曲是“失去和遗憾的凄美歌曲”，补充道：“它抓住了每位听众内心中所拥有的记忆的握柄，将它与阿黛尔自己的戏剧结合起来<ref name="telegraph">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/artists/Adele-Hello-review/|title=Adele, 'Hello', review: 'delivers raw, honest feeling'|website=The Telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2015-10-26|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125054539/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/artists/Adele-Hello-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”一些媒体提到了歌曲及其MV与美国灵魂歌手[[莱昂纳尔·里奇|莱昂纳尔·里奇]]的《Hello》的相似之处<ref name=Horton>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/news/hello-is-it-me-youre-looking-for/|title=Lionel Richie responds to Adele's 'Hello'|accessdate=2015-10-27|date=2015-10-26|first=Helena|last=Horton|work=The Daily Telegraph|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722022912/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/news/hello-is-it-me-youre-looking-for/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2015-10-26/hello-adele-is-it-lionel-richie-youre-looking-for|title=Lionel Richie responds on Instagram to Adele 'Hello' music video mash-up|work=Radio Times|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722022919/https://www.radiotimes.com/news/2015-10-26/hello-adele-is-it-lionel-richie-youre-looking-for/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 商业表现 ==
=== 欧洲和大洋洲 ===
发行后三天，[[英国官方排行榜公司|英国官方排行榜公司]]宣布歌曲在英国已累计165000份排行榜销量，其中有156000份为下载销量<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-34641642|title=Adele heads straight to number one|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124541/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-34641642|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲于2015年10月30日进入[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]榜首，截至2015年11月5日周末，合共销量333000份，其中下载销量占259000份，是近三年来该榜单榜首单曲的最高销量。这是阿黛尔继2011年《[[Someone_like_You_(阿黛尔歌曲)|Someone like You]]》后的第二支英国冠军单曲。此外，歌曲首周流媒体发放732万次，打破之前由[[贾斯汀·比伯|贾斯汀·比伯]]的《[[你什么意思|你什么意思]]》所持有的记录。包括流媒体销售并排除《[[英国版X音素|英国版X音素]]》和《{{le|流行偶像|Pop Idol}}》优胜者的单曲、重要慈善活动唱片和圣诞节冠军单曲，歌曲成为21世纪英国销量第二大的榜首单曲，击败了于2001年2月在单周内卖出345000张的[[夏奇|夏奇]]的《{{le|这可不是我|It Wasn't Me}}》<ref name="UK number 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/adele-smashes-official-chart-records-with-comeback-single-hello__11165/|title=Adele smashes Official Chart records with comeback single Hello|publisher=Official Charts Company|last=Copsey|first=Rob|date=2015-10-30|accessdate=2015-10-30|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117091319/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/adele-smashes-official-chart-records-with-comeback-single-hello__11165/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。接下来的一个星期内，歌曲仍在英国单曲榜上保持榜首位置，又被数字下载121000次、流媒体分发578万次，当周歌曲受到BPI的销量金认证<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/adele-says-hello-to-another-week-at-number-1__11291/|title=Adele says Hello to another week at Number 1|date=2015-11-06|publisher=Official Charts Company|first=Justin|last=Myers|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://archive.is/20151106201229/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/adele-says-hello-to-another-week-at-number-1__11291/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲还在比利时、捷克共和国、法国、德国、希腊、匈牙利、爱尔兰、以色列、意大利、黎巴嫩、卢森堡、荷兰、挪威、葡萄牙、苏格兰、斯洛伐克和瑞士以榜首位置首秀<ref name="idolator7613572">{{cite web|url=http://www.idolator.com/7613572/adele-hello-debuts-chart-hot-100-sells-jaw-dropping-1-million-downloads|script-title=en:Adele’s “Hello” Debuts At #1, Sells Jaw-Dropping 1.1 Million US Downloads In First Week|first1=Robble|last1=Daw|date=2015-11-02|accessdate=2015-11-11|archive-date=2021-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210720085555/https://www.idolator.com/7613572/adele-hello-debuts-chart-hot-100-sells-jaw-dropping-1-million-downloads}}</ref>。

在澳大利亚，歌曲于2015年10月31日进入[[澳大利亚唱片业协会榜|澳大利亚唱片业协会榜]]榜首，卖出超过59075份，使得它发售第一个星期就赢得金认证。歌曲还成为当年第二首卖得最快的单曲，紧随《[[再见你一面|再见你一面]]》之后<ref name="maricrisfaderugao">{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com.au/adeles-hello-hits-platinum-australia-she-prepares-one-televised-concert-1479892|script-title=en:Adele’s ‘Hello’ hits platinum in Australia as she prepares for a one-off televised concert|author=Maricris Faderugao|date=2015-11-03|work=International Business Times AU|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722022940/https://www.ibtimes.com.au/adeles-hello-hits-platinum-australia-she-prepares-one-televised-concert-1479892|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是阿黛尔继2011年的《Someone like You》后<ref name="AUS number 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/news/50690/adele-says-'hello'-to-the-#1-spot-?pos=1|title=Adele says 'Hello' to the No. 1 spot|publisher=ARIA Charts|last=Gavin|first=Ryan|date=2015-10-31|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-date=2015-11-05|archive-url=https://archive.is/20151105034251/http://www.ariacharts.com.au/news/50690/adele-says-'hello'-to-the-%231-spot-?pos=1#1-spot-?pos=1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，第二支在ARIA单曲榜上名列榜首的单曲。单曲在第二个星期继续保持领先位置，凭借7万份的销量获得铂金认证<ref name="maricrisfaderugao"/>。在新西兰，歌曲以榜首位置首秀新西兰单曲榜，并在接下来一周保持该位置，获得铂金认证<ref name="idolator7613572"/>。

=== 北美 ===
在北美，歌曲于2015年11月2日入主[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]榜首，到2015年11月14日，已成为{{le|公告牌百强单曲榜里程碑作品列表|List of Billboard Hot 100 chart achievements and milestones|第24首榜首首秀的歌曲}}。发布三天后，歌曲在电台歌曲榜上以第49位首秀。在电台播放的第一周，歌曲的全格式观众印象从45升至9，增长了146%，达到7000万人。歌曲录得2040万次流媒体点播数，在流媒体歌曲榜名列第一，成为阿黛尔第一首在该榜单上夺冠的歌曲。歌曲凭借111.2万的销量登顶数字歌曲榜，是第一首单周内卖出100万张数字版的歌曲，比截至2009年2月28日周末共卖出63.6万次下载版的[[佛罗·里达|佛罗·里达]]的《{{le|神魂颠倒|Right Round}}》所持有的单周内下载销量最多的唱片几乎要翻一番。歌曲在美国流媒体以6160万起步，成为她第一首在流媒体歌曲榜夺冠和每周销量最多的单曲，仅次于在2013年3月3日周末录得1.03亿流媒体点播量的[[鲍尔_(音乐家)|鲍尔]]的《[[哈林摇|哈林摇]]》<ref name="US number 1">{{cite web|url=http://m.billboard.com/entry/view/id/145909|title=Adele Says "Hello" to No. 1 Debut, First Song To Sell 1 Million Downloads in a Week|work=Billboard|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2015-11-02|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105071255/http://m.billboard.com/entry/view/id/145909|archive-date=2015-11-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。歌曲是第一首单周售出超过100万份数字版的歌曲，是{{le|尼尔森唱片市场调查公司|Nielsen SoundScan}}自1991年追踪销量以来，单周总销量第三大的歌曲。只有[[艾尔顿·约翰|艾尔顿·约翰]]的《{{le|风中的蜡烛1997|Candle in the Wind 1997|风中的蜡烛1997/关于你如何欣赏夜景的事情}}》在单周销量更多——在首周卖出344.6万份，次周121.2份<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.billboard.com/entry/view/id/146220|title=Adele's 'Hello' Has Biggest Sales Week for a Single Since Elton John's Princess Diana Tribute in 1997|author=Gary Trust & Keith Claufield|work=Billboard|date=2015-11-04|accessdate=2015-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216093226/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6752913/adele-hello-biggest-sales-week-elton-john-candle-wind-1997|archive-date=2019-12-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 。

第二周，歌曲在[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]保持榜首位置，又卖出63.5万份数字版，成为单周数字销量第三高的歌曲，也是非首秀周的最佳成绩。歌曲凭借在流媒体上的4740万次点播量，在流媒体歌曲榜上保住榜首位置，但第一个星期为6160万次，同比下降23%，歌曲凭借1810万次流媒体点播量保住最多点播歌曲榜的榜首位置。而在电台歌曲榜，歌曲从9升至6，全格式观众印象升至1.06亿次，同比上涨46%，从而成为在百强单曲榜上的电台热播单曲榜榜首歌曲。歌曲还在成人另类歌曲榜中从第二位挪到第一位，同时在成人当代音乐榜上从第9移到第4<ref name="auto1">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6754159/adele-hello-hot-100-second-week|title=Adele's 'Hello' Tops Hot 100 for Second Week; Ariana Grande, Meghan Trainor Hit Top 10|author=Gary Trust|work=Billboard|date=2015-11-09|accessdate=2015-11-09|archive-date=2016-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925134009/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6754159/adele-hello-hot-100-second-week|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到第三周，歌曲仍在百强榜和数字单曲榜占据榜首位置，数字下载48万次，成为第三首三个星期内销量突破40万份的歌曲。第四个星期歌曲在电台歌曲榜从第6升至第1（是该榜25年的历史上幅度最大的榜首跳跃），成为自1993年8月28日[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]的《[[梦中情人_(玛丽亚·凯莉歌曲)|梦中情人]]》在其第四周占据榜首以来，该榜22年来攀升至榜首位置最快的歌曲。此外，歌曲还成为近三年来第三首在百强单曲榜、数字歌曲榜、流媒体歌曲榜、最多点播歌曲榜和电台歌曲全部五个榜单中同时获得冠军的歌曲<ref name="auto3">{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6762610/adele-hello-hot-100-no-1-third-week-fastest-radio-songs|work=Billboard|title=Adele's 'Hello' Leads Hot 100 for Third Week, Is Fastest Radio Songs No. 1 in 22 Years|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=2015-11-16|accessdate=2015-11-16|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117153214/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6762610/adele-hello-hot-100-no-1-third-week-fastest-radio-songs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。、

歌曲以榜首位置进入[[加拿大百强单曲榜|加拿大百强单曲榜]]，卖出14万份，超过于同一个星期以第二位首秀该榜单、卖出4万份的[[贾斯汀·比伯|贾斯汀·比伯]]的《{{le|对不起 (歌曲)|Sorry (Justin Bieber song)|对不起}}》。歌曲被流媒体点播479万次，创下单周流媒体点播次数最多的纪录<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ajournalofmusicalthings.com/adeles-hello-annihilates-the-competition-in-its-first-week-its-not-even-close/|title=Adele's "Hello" ANNIHILATES the Competition in Its First Week. It's Not Even Close|author=Cross, Alan|date=2015-11-02|accessdate=2015-11-03|publisher=A Journal of Musical Things|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104021527/http://ajournalofmusicalthings.com/adeles-hello-annihilates-the-competition-in-its-first-week-its-not-even-close/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 音乐录像带 ==
{{quote box|width=30%|align=right|quote=“（视频）非常的喧宾夺主。歌词‘你好，是我’之后你看到有人拎起电话。我不擅长构思超级概念的视频。我想她围着屋子转，打通电话，在树林中收尾很不错，或许还要有倒叙。”

—多兰诠释视频的概念<ref name="LATimes"/>}}

歌曲的音乐录影带由[[魁北克|魁北克]]演员兼导演[[泽维尔·多兰|泽维尔·多兰]]执导，于2015年10月22日發布<ref>{{cite news|title=Adele enlists Xavier Dolan for new music video Hello|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/adele-xavier-dolan-1.3283914|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=2015-10-23|date=2015-10-22|archive-date=2015-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024064355/http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/adele-xavier-dolan-1.3283914|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-unveils-25-track-list-plans-hello-video-20151022|last1=Spanos|first1=Brittany|title=Adele Unveils '25' Track List, Plans 'Hello' Video|work=Rolling Stone|date=2015-10-22|accessdate=2015-10-22|archive-date=2018-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180306083502/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/adele-unveils-25-track-list-plans-hello-video-20151022|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片的概念围绕着被阿黛尔称为自己年轻时一位最近分手的女性展开<ref name="LATimes"/>。影片有部分——大多数是结尾处的池塘和开头处阿黛尔睁开双眼的特写——均采用[[IMAX|IMAX]]摄像机拍摄，使得影片成为第一部IMAX格式音乐录影带<ref>{{cite web|date=2015-10-23|last=Rosen|first=Christopher|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/10/23/adele-hello-video|title=Adeles's powerful 'Hello' Video Already Made History|accessdate=2015-10-23|work=Entertainment Weekly|archive-date=2015-10-24|archive-url=https://archive.is/20151024142452/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/10/23/adele-hello-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片灵感出自多兰还没过20歲时所创作的半自传体处子作《[[杀死我阿妈|杀死我阿妈]]》<ref name="LATimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-adele-hello-video-song-flip-phone-20151023-story.html|title=Director of Adele's 'Hello' video explains its look, theme and, oh yes, flip phone|author=Steven Zeitchik|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2015-10-25|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029014614/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-adele-hello-video-song-flip-phone-20151023-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。视频于2015年9月在魁北克一个农场录制。

影片由美国演员[[崔斯坦·瓦尔德斯|崔斯坦·瓦尔德斯]]主演。多兰通过[[Skype|Skype]]聯絡瓦尔德斯，阐述了影片的概念，使得瓦尔德斯同意出演<ref name="ew.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/10/26/adele-hello-tristan-mack-wilds|title=Tristan Mack Wilds on Adele's Hello|work=Entertainment Weekly's EW.com|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722023046/https://ew.com/article/2015/10/26/adele-hello-tristan-mack-wilds/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在拍摄时，阿黛尔和瓦尔德斯被要求即兴“挖掘”各自过去的戀情，好让情感正确表达。多兰还拍摄了阿黛尔和瓦尔德斯说话和欢笑时的镜头。棕褐色调的影片展现阿黛尔在一间小屋内和一片茂密的树林中唱歌的情景，穿插着她含泪通电话和与瓦尔德斯所演角色过去关系的倒叙镜头<ref>{{cite news|last1=Tyrrell|first1=Rebecca|title=The guy in Adele's new music video might look familiar to you|url=http://metro.co.uk/2015/10/23/the-guy-in-adeles-new-music-video-might-look-familiar-to-you-5457876/|accessdate=2015-10-23|work=Metro|date=2015-10-23|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722024521/https://metro.co.uk/2015/10/23/the-guy-in-adeles-new-music-video-might-look-familiar-to-you-5457876/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿黛尔在影片用的{{le|翻盖手机|Flip (form)}}被广泛认为是一种{{le|复古风|Retro style}}。多兰回应评论时表示：“用[[iPhone|iPhone]]拍戏让我很不舒服，因为我觉得我是在拍广告。iPhone、笔记本电话，所有这些杂七杂八的，对我而言，他们把我拉回了現實：那不可是你所想要的。你想要走出自己的生活，你想要进入别人的世界，你想要去某个地方，你想讲一个故事。我意识到或许有翻盖手机做其他事情会更让我分心，但这绝不是故意的！<ref>{{Cite web|title = 'Hello' Music Director Explains Why Adele Uses That Flip Phone|url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/adele-hello-flip-phone_562bd430e4b0aac0b8fd2030|website = The Huffington Post|accessdate = 2015-11-10|archive-date = 2015-11-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117034535/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/adele-hello-flip-phone_562bd430e4b0aac0b8fd2030|dead-url = no}}</ref>”

影片打破了[[Vevo|Vevo Record]]此前的纪录，24小时内点击量高达2770万<ref name="Guardian-Groves"/>。之后，视频继续打破[[麦莉·赛勒斯|麦莉·赛勒斯]]的《[[爱情破坏球|爱情破坏球]]》五天内点击量最快达到1亿的纪录<ref>{{cite web|url=http://de.eonline.com/news/711235/adele-s-hello-music-video-shatters-miley-cyrus-vevo-record|publisher=E!|date=2015-10-29|first= Francesca|last=Bacardi| title=Adele's "Hello" Music Video Shatters Miley Cyrus' Vevo Record}}</ref>。搜索词“Adele hello”于星期五和星期六登顶[[YouTube|YouTube]]搜索热词，头两天每小时平均点击量均达100万次，单个小时点击量高达160万，击败了《[[星球大战：原力觉醒|星球大战：原力觉醒]]》预告片每小时120万的浏览量<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/34659073/people-are-playing-adele-one-million-times-an-hour-on-youtube|title=People are playing Adele one million times an hour on YouTube|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2015-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029043017/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/34659073/people-are-playing-adele-one-million-times-an-hour-on-youtube|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 现场表演 ==
